title: Human - Disgusting Greatness Of People (2014)
description:
HUMAN
Moscow, Russia

The band was founded in 2002 as a one-man project, the first album was recored the same year. A lineup was gathered in 2003 and second album was recorded. After a series of concerts, in 2005 the musicians were dismissed and the author composed the third album (2007) which has not been recorded until now. Human believes to complete this task one day.

Paul "Deadhuman" Kretz - guitars, drums, bass, vocals, fx, mixing and mastering.
